# Project Entry Points and Core Directories

## Frontend Entry Points
- Main Site: [index.html](mdc:index.html)
- Blog Detail Page: [blog/index.html](mdc:blog/index.html)
- Admin Login: [admin/index.html](mdc:admin/index.html)
- Admin Dashboard: [admin/dashboard.html](mdc:admin/dashboard.html)

## Backend (Cloudflare Functions)
- **Public API:** Files within `functions/api/` directory define public endpoints.
- **Admin API & Auth:** Files within `functions/admin/` define protected admin endpoints and handle authentication via [_middleware.js](mdc:functions/admin/_middleware.js).

See [README.md](mdc:README.md) for detailed API routes.
